name: DYRTxTREllExTOM-G (Dreams Come True) CLEAN
description: Hip-Hop R&B Mixed track produced by Multi Platinum producer Rushdee Williams. This track was recorded in Tampa Florida at Glass House Studio. This picture is of me and Rushdee Celebrating his platinum sells on Lil Wayne’s Carter 5. I was inspired by my cousins success and dropped this track when he let me hear this instrumental of this song that night.
